Description: Disk health and S.M.A.R.T. monitoring for Linux
 Puls DiskInfo is a professional-grade disk health monitoring
 application for Linux, inspired by CrystalDiskInfo. It reads
 S.M.A.R.T. data from your drives and presents it in a clear,
 detailed GTK4 interface.
 .
 Features include health status monitoring, temperature tracking,
 complete S.M.A.R.T. attributes display, NVMe health information,
 and support for HDD, SATA SSD, NVMe SSD, USB, and SSHD drives.
